snippet.title: Dropship Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW - https://minigoliath.itch.io/dropship

DROPSHIP is a precision, gravity-bending, flying game that will test your skills and nerves. Use gravity to your advantage and drop to the landing pad before you run out of fuel!

-Tackle 21 increasingly tense levels
-Unlock an additional 4 if you can rescue lost crew members along the way

Post us your best times and clips at https://twitter.com/Mini_Goliath

Thanks for the support!

The Mini Goliath Co.
